		<title>Africa has seen oil shocks before. Why 2026 could be the turning point for clean energy</title>
		<link>https://techcabal.com/2026/05/15/africa-has-seen-oil-shocks-before-2026-could-be-the-turning-point-for-clean-energy-in-africa/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Adedayo Ojo]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Fri, 15 May 2026 12:44:58 +0000</pubDate>
